BGP_Module
    System Requirements
		* 4Suite (later than 1.0_alpha4)
			Follow the instruction from http://4suite.org/
        * Quagga
            Follow the instruction from http://quagga.net
        * Yapps2
            Download the file from http://theory.stanford.edu/~amitp/Yapps/
            UnZip the file
            Add the path of the folder just unzipped to the $PYTHONPATH 

    The modules contains files made by a parser generator, so in order to create the
    files it should be run first 
        ">python setup.py"

    
